body: "GitHub: https://github.com/unbraind/pm-cli/issues/453\n\n## Problem\n`pm plan materialize --json` returns materialized[] entries with only `id`; title/type/parent are undefined in the response projection (data on disk is correct). Callers need a pm get round trip per created item to confirm.\n\n## Proposed fix\nInclude { id, title, type, parent, tags } per materialized entry — same compact projection list rows use.\n\n## Definition of done\nmaterialize --json response carries the confirmation fields; spec updated; no extra reads needed to verify materialization."
